      • assignGameRoleToMember

        private void assignGameRoleToMember(net.dv8tion.jda.core.managers.GuildController controller,
                                    net.dv8tion.jda.core.entities.Member member,
                                    net.dv8tion.jda.core.entities.Game game)
        Checks if a Guild contains a Game Role using guildHasGameRole(Guild, Game), and if the Guild has the Role, assign it to the Member. If the Role does not exist, the method creates the Role and then assigns it to the Member. (If the Member already has the Role, the method does not assign it.)
        Parameters:
        controller - Used to create the Role.
        member - The Member for the Role to be assigned to.
        game - The Game whose name is used in searching/creating the Role.
